 * @param image The image being observed.
 * @param infoflags The bitwise inclusive OR of the following flags:WIDTH, HEIGHT, PROPERTIES, SOMEBITS, FRAMEBITS, ALLBITS, ERROR, ABORT.
 * @param x The x coordinate of the image.
